      "csl:pageColumn": "880,3",
      "rdf:value": "<L>178088<pc>880,3<k1>riP<k2>riP<e>1\r\n<s>riP</s> ¦ <ab>cl.</ab> 6. <ab>P.</ab> (<ls>Dhātup. xxviii, 23</ls>) <s>riPati</s> (<ab>p.</ab> <s>-rePat</s>, <ls>ŚāṅkhBr.</ls>; <ab>pf.</ab> <s>rirePa</s> &c. <ab>Gr.</ab>; <ab>ind.p.</ab> <s>rePitvA</s>, <ls>Pāṇ. i, 2, 23</ls>, <ab>Sch.</ab>),\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to snarl, <ls>AV.</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/> (only <ls>L.</ls>) to speak or boast (<s>kaTane</s> or <s>katTane</s>);\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to blame;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to fight;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to give;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to hurt, kill (<ab>cf.</ab> √ <s>rimP</s>) :\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/><ab>Pass.</ab> <s>riPyate</s>, to be murmured or spoken in a guttural or burring manner (like the letter <s>r</s>);\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/> to have or take the pronunciation of the letter <s>r</s>, <ls>ĀśvŚr.</ls> (<ab>cf.</ab> <s>rePa</s>). <info westergaard=\"riPa,28.23,06.0026\"/><info whitneyroots=\"riP,140\"/><info verb=\"genuineroot\" cp=\"6P\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AriP#record-pwg",
      "@type": "csl:SourceRecord",
